Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that a channeled teaching is necessarily negative. It may well be positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know who is it, you know, what is the level of truth of the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because many people go into, ooh, ah, it's the old Master Baba Dung Dong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, you go, what is the energy of Master Ding Dong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think of a very famous Baba right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baba I'm thinking about, it calibrates over 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,now over 300, over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to calibrate over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we discover new things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We discover new things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the so-called, many of the sort of legendary spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of them are all in India or somewhere in a foreign place or some foreign culture or some foreign time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when you calibrate their energy, it's really negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes you weak, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't want to upset your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to tell them about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always recommend, what you should do is go through your spiritual library.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody here probably has as many books at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those that make you go strong, you put over on this side of the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and all those that make you go weak, you put them on that side of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a profound experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize some things that you never realized before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden you get where spiritual falsehood comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from erroneous context.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a lot of the gurus are very slick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met some of the slickest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They know the right things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have enough spiritual truth in their bag of tricks that they can convince anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason you can't detect it, because what's out is the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the context is out of your range of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not spiritually advanced enough, the third eye isn't open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can see the context out of which the other speaker is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't get what the error is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because the error is outside your,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,outside your vision, you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So being able to calibrate, being able to discern the level of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is very, very, very practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can help you find lost objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it can save your lifetimes of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because following a false guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and then discovering disillusionment at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,can be exquisitely painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisitely, it's probably more painful than losing a loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing a child, I've lost children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,being a spiritual rake is probably the most painful of all human,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,possible human experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That you've been misled by some guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've given up everything for in worship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and believed everything he said to Zoe as a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, because there are teachings like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to make your guru into like a god-like figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender to your guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you find out he's been ripping you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, really savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've seen some patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw one, it took her six pros act a day to hold back the suicidal depression
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that was precipitated when she realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the person that she thought was, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,her sacred guru on earth was just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,taking her for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, his heart chakra was negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the words were all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it didn't come out of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nature and tradition in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Americans are very naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A slick guru, guru-ism, comes out of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slick evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of years of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're more clever than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you can think of, they've already thought about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple thousand years ago and took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way your intellect is going to discern it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Without kundalini-ology, I don't know how anybody can protect himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual rationalizations are so clever and so intriguing and so seductive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's the seduction of false spiritual glamour
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the track to the average spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've come across.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all done all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all studied Reiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've gone to these workshops and those workshops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've followed Master so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We got channelings from so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And psychic readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the magic dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else have we done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic mantras and the cards and all the deal, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everybody in finding out what is spiritual truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a normal thing to check out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's labeled spiritual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they must be spiritual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's Madam so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got Master so-and-so on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she sees that, hmm, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you sit there and your ears are just perked up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're just sure there's some great wisdom of the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's about to be laid on you as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can calibrate the level of truth of the speaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how many readings you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you know the calibration of the channeler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is being channeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she reminded me that the world runs on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quarter to 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what our time schedule is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to start at 1230, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to run from 10 to 1230.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She distracted reality in this world for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know where I was if it weren't for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to her this morning, I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to speak someplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly I feel like this energy comes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a huge deep breath suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the presence intensifies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a feeling of an incredible joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's hard to know where you are in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you're supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're measuring and all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those are the kind of phenomena that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought you would do the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there was, besides the Kundalini positive energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there was very intense spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,something else also,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was almost as though
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as you reach a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you pull up its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was also years of clearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what's out in the human consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,not in my own personal self or karmic background.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was years of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of clearing that which is out in the collective of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a great deal of physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a great deal of the nervous systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,very often wracked with extreme pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,considerable pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,until that particular dilemma was worked through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that used to worry me until,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the Buddha said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said that he had years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in which his body was wracked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as though his bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even his bones ached.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And Susan pointed that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, look at the good ones then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there are various physical phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that go with this intense spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the Course in Miracles extremely much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now we'll resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do we resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what time do we resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1.30?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to quit from 12.30 to 1.30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk more about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I, at one time, taught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew Helen, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the psychologist that she worked with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who died of heart problems, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I have a profound interest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And an understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what we were talking about this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of gives it the concept
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the conceptual context
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in which to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How it is that to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask to see it as it is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all you're really asking for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is to move from perception to vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're really saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if I get out of an arbitrary positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire picture is revealed to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see that there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be solved
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because there isn't any problem to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that out of the wholeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the oneness, the wholeness of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then, vision prevails over perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles are only miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From the viewpoint of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they're only the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing miraculous about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think of a certain thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when you get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's the way it is in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But to the person who spends every day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in Newtonian paradigm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they would term many of these things miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculous became commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the way things work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the nice things about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing this too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you see on the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that all the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,things that calibrate below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all the negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,anger, resentment, self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,well, the calibrated number
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is the logarithm of a relative power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,where is hatred on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is way down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things that are like 100 or less,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what we worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is our negative thoughts and feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritually driven people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,are usually bugged by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what they consider their problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is things that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel bad about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel bad about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you get into self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything negative we feel bad about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're trying to evolve beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know we're in some kind of an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So not only do you feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but you feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was seeing things correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be feeling guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so I must be screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you're guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about being guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual people really have,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,really a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that other people don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They just feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hell with you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and they enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They get,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they like it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't like it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to see this differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they see this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as in truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that he's a hateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,evil person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that I want to get even with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we worry about our negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from the consciousness level here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the log 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,think that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is so weak and puny
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,don't quote me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but you could spend all day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have one loving thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,love your kitty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sweetie pie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're God's little
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gifting mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,man,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you just outdid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,all that negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if that wasn't so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,population
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates below
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,200,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,life would not even
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,be possible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,had the same power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as a loving thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this planet would have
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,blown apart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,millennia ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because 85% of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are walking around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,screw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you son of a bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting even with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an extra dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and kicking old widows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,raise the rent on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,give grannies free pillows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on Medicare,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred and anger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would have absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyed all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The interesting thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll do some drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on the board
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,after this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we said that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind is like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a pyramid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and 85% of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,falls below
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not tied up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,look at that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hanging out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,there all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from this guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,this is magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,this is sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,like it was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're out of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like floating around
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything's still going,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you're tied to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't dare leave
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,this body here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because I won't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to see, hear, feel, think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or enjoy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with just like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,same feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like you're light
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're floating around
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and hear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the physical
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,body lying there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,
