Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:25:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,cows. And I'm getting old enough so I don't care what they do to me. Now is a good time to do it. I'm getting older anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.71,0:25:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I got shot for the Enterprise. I'm just kidding, but we will address some
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.39,0:25:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,sacred cows. Because why does ignorance prevail century after century?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.99,0:25:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Such profound ignorance blinds mankind. You know, mankind is just newly sprouted,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,newly sprouted. And what prevails primarily is profound ignorance in just
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,about every level of human endeavor. Modern society only started a couple
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hundred years ago. I mean in time it's like yesterday. So, how does such
