Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.96,1:12:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and his caring about his people,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.10,1:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,his caring about his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.78,1:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that all we're asking him to do
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.18,1:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is to open his heart to his own people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.72,1:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we're asking him to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.32,1:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not telling him what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.14,1:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not telling him anything that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.40,1:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything wrong with his society at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.18,1:13:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His society has evolved to a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.22,1:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.16,1:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.04,1:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.66,1:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we as a group can certainly potentiate its growth,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.00,1:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.79,1:13:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All in agreement?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.58,1:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All in favor of turning China around?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.46,1:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody opposed?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.61,1:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Greatest thing that ever happened in Chinese history
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.51,1:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,has just happened in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.71,1:13:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.25,1:13:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.19,1:13:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to tell them,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.61,1:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because that would set up a defense, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.39,1:13:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to set up a defense, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.27,1:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we said, we as a group are praying for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.05,1:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you people,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.59,1:13:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it would set up enormous resistance there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.29,1:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these goddamn Americans trying to tell us how to end the crisis?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.21,1:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were civilized by then.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.11,1:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You people were still hanging around in trees,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.81,1:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.89,1:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was a Chinaman, I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.01,1:13:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what, that's what folks were still hanging in trees,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.73,1:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for God's sake, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.41,1:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how the American attitude sets other people on edge.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.39,1:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a little embarrassing, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.85,1:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A little embarrassing at times.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.41,1:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the lack of humility,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.57,1:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to a great leader with great potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.85,1:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to move his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.09,1:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it happen in North Korea, so I know it can happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.01,1:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also know that we have the capacity to do that with China.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.81,1:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.10,1:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said it so much, China.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.64,1:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can raise the level of the consciousness of the leader of China
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.16,1:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by over 10 points' resist, by 20 points' resist,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.00,1:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by 30 points' resist, holy Christ, by 50 points' resist, oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.80,1:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So this group, they're, you know, not necessarily meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.24,1:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're buttering your toast, you can just think,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.28,1:14:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,gosh, you're not such a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.78,1:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.92,1:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You butter your toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.44,1:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that we can raise his level of consciousness 40 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.28,1:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enormous, enormous, 40 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.38,1:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,30.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.93,1:14:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an incredible jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.23,1:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it would.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.24,1:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we being grandiose?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.10,1:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we being real?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.30,1:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being real.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.32,1:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what happens is you deny your own divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.06,1:15:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.56,1:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm not of divine essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.12,1:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.87,1:15:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What allows you to be an ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.11,1:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People like me, they wouldn't have the power
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.21,1:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to influence the future of a giant, the biggest country on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.31,1:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chinese are what, one and a half billion people
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.21,1:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or two billion people or something out of the six billion that exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.20,1:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this little group of people here in nowhere California,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.26,1:15:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to shift the whole .
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.40,1:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.54,1:15:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.12,1:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the miraculous, there's nothing to the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.59,1:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.45,1:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is the way that it wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.34,1:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is what brought us together and brought up this subject so that we should do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.28,1:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God said, gee, I need a group to get together and help out China there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.71,1:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you bringing it up, Dave, at your next talk?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.17,1:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.89,1:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It only came to me as I said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.63,1:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I never know what I'm going to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.44,1:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it as it's said.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.81,1:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no knowing that it's going to be said.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.49,1:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And usually there's no recognition that it was said.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.89,1:16:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I depend on her to recall that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.59,1:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that which erupts of its own is out of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.83,1:16:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.25,1:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by the energy of it that it's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.95,1:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.74,1:16:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective power of the divinity within each and every one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.20,1:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed out as love towards that country and its leader will have a profound influence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.56,1:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.01,1:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To deny it is to deny your own reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.45,1:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to say, I'm only a weak ego and I have no influence in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.29,1:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.09,1:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a toad.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.29,1:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.47,1:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of us here reflects the divinity of God expressed through our own beingness in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.46,1:17:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good karma time, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.98,1:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this one, wrap this one up for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.38,1:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get there, you can say, yep, we were part of what pulled the chain out of the mud, you know, and got them sailing again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.67,1:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just the joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.17,1:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the joy of one's existence, the joy of one's existence is the joy of the awareness of the reality of that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.07,1:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.61,1:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you begin to own the power of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.81,1:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of everyone here is Christ-like in that by thinking of that in a loving way,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.77,1:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in a loving way, for our love of the people of China, Lord, many miserable,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.47,1:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and our love for the leader, see, because I found out one thing about these great leaders,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.47,1:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is many of them have great power, but the heart isn't open yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.11,1:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart isn't open.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.57,1:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart isn't open yet, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.50,1:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And they really are concerned, and they are very, very capable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.76,1:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of these people are political geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.42,1:18:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not fools, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.58,1:18:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hitler was a political genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.68,1:18:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he wrapped your friend's finger like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.06,1:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's out then is the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.10,1:18:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's out is the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.32,1:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you radiate the knowingness of that, the divinity of that intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.97,1:18:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're inviting that beingness to respond to your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.51,1:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And against love, there is no defense.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.03,1:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Against coercion, there's many defenses.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.54,1:18:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So to try to coerce the Chinese into the American way is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.34,1:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the leader of China is telling me, what's his name, the interviewer there,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.97,1:18:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he said, what's his name again?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.37,1:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.97,1:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.47,1:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.97,1:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like criticizing China, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.77,1:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,China, thousands and thousands of years old, and here's Mike Wallace telling this guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.91,1:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you folks straighten up, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.41,1:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the leader of China looks at Wallace and he says, there are many things in your society
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.13,1:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that do not necessarily meet our approval either.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.43,1:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs, sex, violence, gangs, I mean, there's a few things, graffiti that we don't care for in China.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.32,1:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock music, kill, murder, and rape your mother, and slice up your sister,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.16,1:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch the blood squirt all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.66,1:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you listen to the lyrics of some of these things, you say, I don't believe that our kids are listening to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.96,1:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sitting there with earphones on, a hypnotic trance, they're a little bit stoned,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.46,1:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're getting programmed, programmed, programmed, programmed, programmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.36,1:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill, kill, kill, kill, and then they go out to their video game and they kill 10 or 20,000 times more,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.96,1:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they appear on the front page of the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.56,1:20:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.46,1:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I just wanted to see what it felt like to kill somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.46,1:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see what it was like to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.16,1:20:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What I've been doing all day, every day for years and years, Mom and Dad,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.66,1:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the music that are being poured into my ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.66,1:20:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what the leader of China was objecting to.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.89,1:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I got instantly, intuitively what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.89,1:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying, no, after looking at your society, we have downsides.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.89,1:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He admitted he had downsides to his society.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.39,1:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have downsides.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.39,1:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have areas in which we can improve, and you likewise, so don't be throwing stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.02,1:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's really saying is, those who live in glass houses shouldn't throw stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.02,1:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.02,1:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was too diplomatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.02,1:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace doesn't have that degree of diplomacy, but the leader of China held back.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.02,1:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He held back.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.02,1:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't lash out at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.02,1:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have, you know, he could have taken Wallace apart, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.02,1:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He held back and said, well, there are a few things about your society
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.02,1:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that we don't necessarily want, you know, to happen within ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.02,1:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And without mentioning anything in specific.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.02,1:21:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what it means then is that the man did, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.21,1:21:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he did...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.21,1:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like he did have his heart there with the interview with Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.24,1:21:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Wallace overlooked his heart completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.24,1:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so into moral superiority, you know, the puritanical positionality that we get into
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.24,1:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.94,1:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What most people in our society consider to be spirituality or religion is nothing but
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.94,1:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,puritanism.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.94,1:21:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Puritanism is not spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.17,1:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Puritanism is not even ethics.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.17,1:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Puritanism is a distortion of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.52,1:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's based upon the duality of right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.94,1:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can't see the people of China as either right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.80,1:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We see them as needful of our love and our consideration.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.80,1:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And certainly the leader, I felt he had his heart there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.80,1:21:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then his heart was turned down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.80,1:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have been turned on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.80,1:22:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd had a chance to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.80,1:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, you know, I really admire your country.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.22,1:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I admire your great culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.22,1:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've made progress in what we consider to be spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.22,1:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we consider to be certain areas that are significant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.22,1:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's probably not time for them to consider that to be significant first.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.22,1:22:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First you've got to have a working society.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.22,1:22:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you try to upgrade its spiritual positions on things.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.28,1:22:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more the way he may be looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.28,1:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.34,1:22:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I wish I'd been up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.34,1:22:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't get a chance to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.34,1:22:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'd like to just win him over and tell him I dearly love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.34,1:22:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe China would have changed by today already, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.34,1:22:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, everybody is vulnerable to love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.34,1:22:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is vulnerable to love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.34,1:22:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of China is extremely vulnerable to love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.34,1:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my intuition.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.34,1:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.34,1:22:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of China is vulnerable to love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.69,1:22:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart chakra is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.30,1:22:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart chakra is already over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.77,1:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't have to turn around somebody who's negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.77,1:23:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to turn around a monster at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.76,1:23:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart is already in the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.76,1:23:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't ask how high.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.76,1:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But certainly our love is sent to him and sent especially to his heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.76,1:23:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His love for his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.76,1:23:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's his opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.76,1:23:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, his opening is his love for his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.76,1:23:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.76,1:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His opening is his love for his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.84,1:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.06,1:23:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was Gorbachev's opening too, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.06,1:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorbachev, when he calibrated his heart chakra, very enormous, 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.22,1:23:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the love for his people, he gave up his political positionality, communism.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.70,1:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the leader of China will do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.70,1:23:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of his love for his people, through his heart, that's his opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.82,1:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And we pour our love into him, and he will pour it back out onto his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.82,1:23:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see a transformation in society.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.82,1:23:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Without throwing a single brick, without firing a single shot, we in this room have
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.82,1:23:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just changed history.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.82,1:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.62,1:23:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have indeed just changed history.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.54,1:24:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have indeed just changed history.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.54,1:24:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.54,1:24:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so it comes about spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.86,1:24:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work is not just personal progress and calibrating how my little consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.09,1:24:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is going as compared to last month and that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.09,1:24:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work is a response to a person.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.66,1:24:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Responsibility towards mankind in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.66,1:24:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the spirit of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.66,1:24:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very responsible for the people in China.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.66,1:24:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.66,1:24:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because very few groups have the insight, the knowledge, the tools, you know what I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.86,1:24:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.86,1:24:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The motivation.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.86,1:24:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How many groups on the planet are committing themselves to this little project today?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.05,1:24:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody want to guess?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.05,1:24:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is another group committed, just as we are today, resistant.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.59,1:24:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're committing themselves to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.59,1:24:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.59,1:24:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.59,1:24:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.59,1:24:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there could be more groups
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.10,1:24:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,spawned out by us.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.28,1:24:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We could spawn out other groups
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.92,1:24:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.62,1:24:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it sort of a local
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.88,1:25:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Course in Miracles project
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.00,1:25:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for the year 2001.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.44,1:25:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Course in Miracles 2001.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.84,1:25:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our project this year is...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.22,1:25:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I dearly love the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.46,1:25:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk more about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.92,1:25:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's 10 to 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.08,1:25:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what we're supposed to do now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.96,1:25:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we ask for some questions
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.66,1:25:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and answers or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.88,1:25:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to see how to do kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.24,1:25:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.72,1:25:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Work what with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.79,1:25:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.47,1:25:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, let me just mention kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.65,1:25:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's a useful tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.51,1:25:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the greatest discoveries
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.83,1:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history of mankind, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.65,1:26:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How to tell truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.85,1:26:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which no man has ever had up until now,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.61,1:26:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,right, in the recent days.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.55,1:26:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You find somebody that you can work with.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.45,1:26:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start like we're just
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.79,1:26:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,starting.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.97,1:26:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.55,1:26:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.29,1:26:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep forgetting that I'm on even here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.73,1:26:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now, when you pick somebody you want to work with,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.87,1:26:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the best thing to do, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.45,1:26:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't want music in the background.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.83,1:26:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to influence people with visual images.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.85,1:26:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think the test person would be best to close their eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.99,1:26:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because as you know, anybody who's read John Dinah's work,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.99,1:26:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you just look at a curve like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.09,1:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it will make you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.25,1:26:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at a curve that goes
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.33,1:26:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,like this, it will make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.41,1:26:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So even looking at something could have an influence.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.87,1:26:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No jewelry across the midline and what do you do
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.80,1:26:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get into that space?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.28,1:26:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no jewelry, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.02,1:26:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, you'll have to talk into this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.80,1:27:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you do when you go into the space.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.90,1:27:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say, let's check something out,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you go through?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.60,1:27:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.96,1:27:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I close my eyes and try and relax and try
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.66,1:27:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and clear the line of any outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.43,1:27:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then just let the.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.81,1:27:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now we sort of recently discovered
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.12,1:27:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that the first question, the first thing you should do is ask
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.40,1:27:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the person to hold in mind somebody they love.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.40,1:27:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, we're going to all do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.24,1:27:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to show you first what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.62,1:27:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to go ones and twos and we'll all do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.98,1:27:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold in mind somebody you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.00,1:27:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be your kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.70,1:27:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hold in mind my kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.16,1:27:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.19,1:27:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the first thing is love makes you go strong
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.27,1:27:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is not love.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.31,1:27:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.37,1:27:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of hatred?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.82,1:27:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.88,1:27:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.37,1:28:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of hatred?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.21,1:28:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.83,1:28:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets harder after a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.14,1:28:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of something negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.84,1:28:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.84,1:28:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of all of those little kids dying in Africa of AIDS.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.09,1:28:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.95,1:28:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.95,1:28:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We're running out of negatives.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.95,1:28:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.66,1:28:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you keep using a negative example
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.82,1:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the person go weak, you yourself are starting
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.08,1:28:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to radiate energy to that which used to make you,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.26,1:28:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, go negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.72,1:28:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know there are images, negative images
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.78,1:28:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that used to make people go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.98,1:28:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I used them in front of thousands of people
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.66,1:28:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in many, many lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.00,1:28:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't do it anymore because of constantly referring to them
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.14,1:28:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and using them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.38,1:28:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Their energy has actually shifted to the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.01,1:28:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a group we were going to test that used
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.57,1:28:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.39,1:28:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, makes you have to go strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.03,1:28:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.99,1:28:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of, of course, miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.07,1:28:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Its power can be demonstrated and calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.17,1:29:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So love makes you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.18,1:29:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is not love makes you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.78,1:29:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.84,1:29:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's divide into ones and twos and we'll go
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.88,1:29:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,through a real quick drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.42,1:29:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go and divide into ones and twos.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.94,1:29:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you that want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.12,1:29:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that don't want to do it, don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.78,1:29:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down and don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.00,1:29:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.72,1:29:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.16,1:29:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.70,1:29:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.92,1:29:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just pick a partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.62,1:29:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide who's going to be number one,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.06,1:29:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who's going to be number two.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.58,1:29:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's ever the oldest gets to be number one?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.16,1:29:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.36,1:29:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever the oldest is, is, is the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.28,1:29:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the youngest one is the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.10,1:29:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.50,1:29:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at your patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.54,1:29:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Patient, hold out your arm to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.22,1:29:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Patient, hold out your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.92,1:29:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.52,1:29:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, doctor, you're going to press down on, on,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.60,1:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,on her wrist with two fingers and say resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.48,1:29:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Say resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.24,1:29:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist. Two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.84,1:29:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? You're not trying to push their arm down out of strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.94,1:30:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to get a feeling for their relative,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.16,1:30:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, strength, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.84,1:30:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You push down with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.48,1:30:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person, I want the patient to push back equal
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.04,1:30:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to the pressure downward, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.98,1:30:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I press down with two fingers, she pushes back equal
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.80,1:30:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so that her arm neither goes up nor down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.76,1:30:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.94,1:30:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more, the harder I press down,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.80,1:30:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the harder she would have to push back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.56,1:30:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you only, you don't need a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.80,1:30:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You just, you just want to get a feeling
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.30,1:30:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say to her, resist, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.98,1:30:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See how easy that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.00,1:30:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not, it's not a hard deal, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.56,1:30:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of an easy thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.64,1:30:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an easy going thing, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.62,1:30:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Now I say to the person, and don't forget now,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.27,1:30:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,patients, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.93,1:30:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now hold in mind, patients, hold in mind somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.61,1:30:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you love and doctors tell them to resist and press down on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.96,1:30:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody go strong with love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.95,1:30:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, okay, patients, I want you to hold the opposite in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.21,1:31:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the little starving kids in Viapra.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.45,1:31:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold somebody you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.63,1:31:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture your favorite pet being run over by a truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.95,1:31:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
