Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.24,1:35:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she is, she's a good test subject.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.24,1:36:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what is the value of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.24,1:36:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the value of this, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.74,1:36:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the value is rather profound.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.24,1:36:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the value of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.24,1:36:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just talk while you're experimenting.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.24,1:36:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to share with you today
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.24,1:36:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're gonna run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.24,1:36:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first learned kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.24,1:36:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do it all over the place, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.24,1:36:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thousands of doctors all over tried it out
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.24,1:36:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we tried to trick it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.24,1:36:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we tried all kinds of tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.24,1:36:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying to disprove it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.24,1:36:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we were all trying to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.24,1:36:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we were all trying to check out its validity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.74,1:36:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was gonna give a lecture on kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.74,1:36:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to a group that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.74,1:37:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who started the first attitudinal healing center?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.24,1:37:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.24,1:37:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.24,1:37:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Jerry, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.24,1:37:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Jane Polsky and his whole crew had come to my house
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.24,1:37:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in Long Island and they spent the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.24,1:37:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're glad they're in heaven, they said.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.24,1:37:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Jane Polsky shared with us
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.24,1:37:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how they were using it as attitudinal healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.24,1:37:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the second attitudinal healing group
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.24,1:37:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States was started in Long Island
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.24,1:37:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,at the clinic I was running at the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.24,1:37:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I started an attitudinal healing center there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.24,1:37:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual, the Course in Miracles group there
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.24,1:37:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,act as facilitators and so we started
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.24,1:37:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the second attitudinal healing center.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.24,1:37:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And to help us get it started,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.24,1:37:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we had Jerry Jane Polsky and his staff
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.24,1:37:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,come and train us and share with us
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.24,1:37:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what he knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.07,1:37:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one night I was gonna give a lecture on kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.39,1:38:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was in my office in Long Island,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.39,1:38:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a huge clinic there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.39,1:38:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And some of my friends who were doing
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.39,1:38:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles were in another adjoining room.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.58,1:38:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I had a break between patients and I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.58,1:38:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I gotta give a lecture on kinesiology tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.58,1:38:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need a couple of volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.16,1:38:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you folks?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.16,1:38:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I had two or three of them and I knew them
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.16,1:38:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I tried the standard things
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.16,1:38:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for which kinesiology was first used.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.16,1:38:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluorescent lights make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.16,1:38:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the common things?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.16,1:38:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pesticides make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.16,1:38:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things that make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.16,1:38:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, I was testing out some of these people
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.16,1:38:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they happened to be working
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.16,1:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the attitudinal healing center.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.16,1:38:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, come on here a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.16,1:38:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And they said they'd be happy to help me
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.16,1:38:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with the lecture tonight, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.16,1:38:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I would have them look at the fluorescent light
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.16,1:38:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.16,1:38:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.16,1:38:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had them look at pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.16,1:39:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the pesticide in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.16,1:39:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't make them go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.16,1:39:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Artificial sweeteners, artificial cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.16,1:39:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that makes people go weak
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.16,1:39:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,had no effect on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.73,1:39:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.73,1:39:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we discovered that once a person,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.73,1:39:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in doing the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.73,1:39:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,once you get past about less than 90 or so,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.73,1:39:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,all the things that make everybody else
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.83,1:39:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe go weak
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.83,1:39:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.83,1:39:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They no longer have any power over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.83,1:39:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then I had a chance to research it out
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.14,1:39:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because a couple of other people I knew
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.14,1:39:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd recommended, I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.14,1:39:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you do the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.14,1:39:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,had started the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.14,1:39:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a chance to check them out
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.14,1:39:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.14,1:39:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,before they did the course
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.14,1:39:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then periodically as they went through
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.14,1:39:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.14,1:39:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did the same thing with Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.14,1:39:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they reached about,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.45,1:39:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's actually less than 76,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.45,1:39:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's around,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.45,1:39:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time you get to less than 90,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.45,1:39:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,all the things that once made you go weak
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.45,1:39:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,won't make you go weak anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.45,1:39:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only subject to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.74,1:40:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've disempowered
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.74,1:40:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world has any power over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.12,1:40:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing out there that has any power over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.12,1:40:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can't just go and do less than 76
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.89,1:40:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then expect this miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.89,1:40:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to go through the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.89,1:40:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And, but we noticed by less than 90,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.89,1:40:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if we'd taken, if we'd gotten
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.31,1:40:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to the lobby there and grabbed somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.31,1:40:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and had them come in here
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.31,1:40:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at the fluorescent light,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.31,1:40:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they would go weak, I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.92,1:40:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we take the people here
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.92,1:40:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who have gone beyond less than 90,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.92,1:40:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, fluorescent light will not make you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.92,1:40:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,go weak anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.92,1:40:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pesticides will not make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.92,1:40:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not subject to.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.97,1:40:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I discovered that, I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.97,1:40:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,well, in that case,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.97,1:40:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,my belief in poison ivy is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.97,1:40:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I said, I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.23,1:40:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to poison ivy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.23,1:40:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it did put me in the hospital a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.23,1:40:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went out and I picked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.23,1:40:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out and picked it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.23,1:40:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and, in fact, I dug it up
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.23,1:40:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it in flower pots
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.23,1:40:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and had it around the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.23,1:40:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I could play with poison ivy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.23,1:41:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It had no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.23,1:41:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.42,1:41:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, things that kill bugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.42,1:41:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,pesticides, sprays, or whatever you call them,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.42,1:41:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,would always give me migraine headaches.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.42,1:41:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to be driven home from the hospital one time
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.42,1:41:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with a migraine headache that was so severe,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.42,1:41:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it was unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.42,1:41:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from exclaiming for pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.42,1:41:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, at that point,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.48,1:41:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,also pesticides had no hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.48,1:41:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.48,1:41:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can demonstrate the effectiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.48,1:41:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Course in Miracles by,
