Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.60,1:46:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of looking at him in any negative, there's no point to look at him in any negative way at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.68,1:46:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's where he is, and what he's waiting for is, he doesn't have the energy, you know, no, he doesn't have the love energy.
