Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.13,1:50:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a busy afternoon. We just saved a third of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.97,1:50:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can't do it. I know we can. It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.46,1:50:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what I believe in is putting the spiritual belief into actual experiential reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.60,1:50:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known people who have gone around in metaphysical groups for 40 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.00,1:50:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're still in the same position they were.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.34,1:50:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still in the same position they were the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.50,1:50:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you have to hear truth? Once. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.62,1:50:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hear it 42 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.62,1:50:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear it once. Make it work once. Now you're done forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.62,1:50:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in taking the course of miracles over again. Is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.36,1:51:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality of who you are stands forth and radiates from this group right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.36,1:51:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you own it, in this instant of time, you never have to ask it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.36,1:51:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.71,1:51:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how enlightenment occurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.71,1:51:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is the absolute grasping of reality.
